=head1 DESCRIPTION

Represents the customer associated with the AWS opportunity. This field
captures key details about the customer that are necessary for managing
the opportunity.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Contacts => ArrayRef[L<Paws::PartnerCentralSelling::Contact>]

Provides a list of customer contacts involved in the opportunity. These
contacts may include decision makers, influencers, and other
stakeholders within the customer's organization.



